data.description: Act Fast! Just like new and ready to immediately be enjoyed featuring 3 bedrooms 2 baths and 2 car-carport with plenty of parking space for your guest. Home was completely remodeled by the present owners. Updates include flooring, electrical, granite counter tops, plumbing fixtures, along with interior/exterior fresh paint, new shutters & new cedar posts. This beautiful brick home is nestled in a large 1.05 acre tract of land with a good size storage building, above ground pool, fun play house, and well kept chicken coop. Plus a 50 AMP camper plug for all your traveling needs. The front porch and covered patio view tranquil open pastures fantastic for outside entertaining. But don’t forget delay may mean disappointment.
